No prior formulation of this specific constraint, in this form, has been identified. This document, and the git commit history of this repository, constitute the timestamped record of this claim — verifiable by anyone, independent of any statement made here about it.

This is a hypothesis offered for testing, not a settled result. Status: Formalism — the inequality has a precise shape and a defined threshold candidate; the named quantities (C, I, A) are not yet independently measured with agreed instruments in any deployed system. Treat accordingly.

